title: #140: An Open Secret With Matt Valentinas
description:
Thank you for tuning in for another episode of Tin Foil Hat With Sam Tripoli. This episode we welcome from the mind-blowing documentary "An Open Secret," Matt Valentinas, to discuss his movie and Hollywood's dark dark secret!
